name: NEW KRYPTO KICKS - Series 01, #07 - "Technology Quiz" by Richard F. Yates
description:
[Digital drawing over photograph of an obsolete technology!]

Do YOU know what that weird, little piece of software is? It's called a "mini-disc," and it was used for storing and playing music---for a while. DESPITE the fact that the very disc sitting on that table was nearly 25 years old, it still played crystal clear!!! Ain't that wonderful??? ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
